flowchart TD
    A([Primary authentication succeeds]) --> B{User already has active MFA?}
    B -- Yes --> C[Complete MFA challenge]
    C --> D{Challenge successful?}
    D -- No --> E[Retry or restart login]
    D -- Yes --> F[Receive full session]
    B -- No --> G{Restricted MFA enabled or re-enrollment required?}
    G -- No --> F
    G -- Yes --> H[Receive restricted enrollment session]
    H --> I[Choose TOTP or secondary email]
    I --> J{TOTP selected?}
    J -- Yes --> K[Scan QR code]
    K --> L[Enter authenticator code]
    J -- No --> M[Enter secondary email]
    M --> N[Receive email OTP]
    N --> O[Enter email OTP]
    L --> P{Verification valid?}
    O --> P
    P -- No --> Q[Show error and retry]
    Q --> I
    P -- Yes --> R[MFA method activated]
    R --> S[Continue login or sign in again]
    S --> F
    F --> T([Access HRMS])
